  "text": "We have developed a 3D hydrogel culture system that supports clonal expansion of DP cells as spheroids and have shown that the spheroids can contribute to hair follicle-inducing activity in vivo. Our approach contrasts with previously reported 3D cultures, in which DP spheres are formed through aggregation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
